      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUAY GAMBLER (8) scored (23.65) last time out over 390m at Q Lakeside four months ago. Well placed here and will can go close with a clear run. OLIVIA SAID NO (4) is a first starter from the Patrick Lavis kennel by Kinloch Brae out of Rockin' Georgia. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Has a nice profile and expected to measure up at first outing. BEST ON LINE (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 411m behind Recruit (24.29) in a Maiden. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. One of the main contenders. ROBELL ZOE (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
